story='On the way up from lunch one day, I decided to press the {number} floor button on the elevator. {Classmate} looked at me in concern as we heard a {adjective_1} noise. When the doors opened, a {adjective_2} {animal} wielding a(n) {fruit} was awaiting on the other side. Quickly {Classmate} pressed the close door button. However, {instructor} exclaimed, "there are snacks on the other side!", so we rushed off past the {animal} right as it lunged into the elevator. "That was close!" {classmate_2} sighed {adverb}. When we came to the promised land, however, {number_2} Googlers stopped us. "You can\'t have your precious snacks unless you solve my {programming }"'
